OL,3,C'Sense of despair' at violent jail put
OL,4,Cinto special measures by watchdog
OL,6,FA "filthy" prison where six prisoners
OL,7,Fwere assaulted or stabbed during their
OL,8,Ffirst night in jail this year has been
OL,9,Fplaced into emergency measures by a
OL,10,Fwatchdog.
OL,12,FChief inspector of prisons Charlie
OL,13,FTaylor has served an urgent
OL,14,Fnotification for HMP Swaleside in Kent
OL,15,Fafter discovering dangerously unsafe
OL,16,Fconditions for prisoners and staff in
OL,17,Fan unannounced visit earlier this
OL,18,Fmonth.
