OL,3,C'Sense of despair' at violent jail put
OL,4,Cinto special measures by watchdog
OL,6,FPrison inspectors heard from inmates
OL,7,Fat the Category B jail who were too
OL,8,Ffrightened to go to health
OL,9,Fappointments or use the gym because of
OL,10,Ffears of violence.
OL,12,FIn a letter to Justice Secretary David
OL,13,FLammy issuing the notice, Mr Taylor
OL,14,Fdescribed "very high levels of
OL,15,Fviolence" as affecting every aspect of
OL,16,Fprison life, with a third of prisoners
OL,17,Fsurveyed saying they had been
OL,18,Fassaulted and three quarters felt
OL,19,Funsafe.
OL,26,@vD@KOUwD@IO]
