OL,3,C'Sense of despair' at violent jail put
OL,4,Cinto special measures by watchdog
OL,6,FDrug-taking was "rife", drones were
OL,7,Fregularly dropping contraband into the
OL,8,Fprison, including knives, and
OL,9,Finspectors also saw widespread
OL,10,Fgraffiti, fire damage, broken
OL,11,Ffurniture and mouldy showers.
OL,13,FAttempts to restore order were also
OL,14,Fdescribed as "wholly insufficient and
OL,15,Finhumane" as a new regime allowed 44%
OL,16,Fof the prison's inmates out of their
OL,17,Fcells for only 30 minutes on most
OL,18,Fweekdays.
