OL,3,C'Sense of despair' at violent jail put
OL,4,Cinto special measures by watchdog
OL,6,FMr Taylor also said it was "shameful"
OL,7,Fsuch a risky prison had been left
OL,8,Fwithout a permanent governor in charge
OL,9,Ffor many months in 2024 and 2025.
OL,11,F"Many hardworking staff were doing an
OL,12,Fimpressive job in extremely difficult
OL,13,Fcircumstances, but during our
OL,14,Finspection we were very troubled by a
OL,15,Fpalpable level of tension and a
OL,16,Fpervasive sense of despair in the
OL,17,Fjail," he said.
OL,26,@nD@\OUnD@eO]sD@AOUyD@FO]
