OL,3,C'Sense of despair' at violent jail put
OL,4,Cinto special measures by watchdog
OL,6,F"The appalling outcomes we found at
OL,7,FSwaleside, holding some of the most
OL,8,Fdangerous men in the country,
OL,9,Frepresent serious failings by leaders
OL,10,Fin the Prison Service to address the
OL,11,Fsystemic problems at this troubled
OL,12,Fjail."
OL,14,FThe emergency measure was introduced
OL,15,Fin 2017 as a way to raise immediate
OL,16,Fconcerns following an inspection,
OL,17,Fwhich requires a response and action
OL,18,Fplan by the Justice Secretary within
OL,19,F28 days.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@FO]
