OL,3,C'Sense of despair' at violent jail put
OL,4,Cinto special measures by watchdog
OL,6,FOther sites issued with an urgent
OL,7,Fnotification include HMP Pentonville,
OL,8,FExeter, Cookham Wood Young Offender
OL,9,FInstitution, Oakhill Secure Training
OL,10,FCentre, Woodhill, Bedford, Wandsworth,
OL,11,FRochester, Manchester and Winchester.
OL,13,FReacting to the latest notice, Prison
OL,14,FReform Trust deputy director Mark Day
OL,15,Fsaid: "It is shocking that a prison
OL,16,Ftasked with the care and
OL,17,Frehabilitation of men serving some of
OL,18,Fthe longest sentences on the estate
OL,19,Fhas been allowed to descend to such an
OL,20,Fappalling level.
OL,26,@wD@GOU
