OL,3,C'Sense of despair' at violent jail put
OL,4,Cinto special measures by watchdog
OL,6,F"We know from our own work at the
OL,7,Fprison that the climate of despair and
OL,8,Fhopelessness amongst prisoners is
OL,9,Fpalpable."
OL,11,FHoward League for Penal Reform chief
OL,12,Fexecutive Andrea Coomber KC said:
OL,13,F"This is the latest in a long line of
OL,14,Finspections that reveal the level of
OL,15,Fdisorder that exists in a prison
OL,16,Fsystem on the brink of collapse.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@JO]uD@AOU
